br />\nVersion 2019.09.04"},{"pid":"870bd7bd2f236431e7422be837105c8b16bb2765","tid":1537481,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:13:04.000Z","msg":"收野阿喂～香港自由之書又出黎收野喇，入黎睇下今次收咩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535646/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535646/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[澄清]國難五金課金問題&mdash;照舊課！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1521564/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1521564/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n國難五金專訪 [國難老闆同一眾員工已保釋,開鋪事直請留意國難五金FB]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1521301/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1521301/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nFB: 國難五金, 香港自由之書"}]}